---
title: Pork & Roasted Veggie Farfalle with Parmesan & Parsley
description: In this dish, we've teamed the traditional Italian tomato sauce with seasoned pork mince and roasted veggies for a meal that
looks every bit as good as it tastes. First dibs gets an extra sprinkling of Parmesan!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tuscan-pork-roasted-veggie-spaghetti-e36c61f9.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/pork-roasted-veggie-farfalle-6115cd4b166ab6099b32f1e0-516a2497.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/pork-and-roasted-veggie-farfalle-6115cd4b166ab6099b32f1e0
time required: 35 minutes
course: main course
nutrition:
  fat: 28.9 g
